      "text": "the U. S. Olympic trials in fancy diving in 1932; I was a Red Cross Life",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Saving Examiner during the years of 1932, '33 and '34. I taught swimming",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
